{"lastModified":1751553445190,"uri":"c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nThis luxury class boat, which was renovated in 2016 and is 34 meters long and 8 meters wide, provides quality service to our valued guests for your blue cruises. For our guests who prefer a quiet and peaceful blue voyage, away from noise and crowds, this gulet is ready for your service, starting from Bodrum port. With 2 Master, 2 Double, 2 Triple cabin options, each cabin has air conditioning, a shower cabin, an en-suite bathroom and a home-style toilet. At the same time, our wifi internet service is unlimited in order not to be disconnected from internet life during your holiday. Our boat has an extremely humble crew, an experienced captain, a very good cook and 2 sailors. With this boat , you can experience your blue voyage as you dreamed, on the routes from Bodrum to Gökova Gulf or Hisarönü Gulf.","blueprint":{"name":"GRANDE MARE","images":["/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a29acf40-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b00ae750-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b18a0d40-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b46cbad0-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b7125f60-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b823f670-d7ae-11ee-bb06-2ba0e5c0e244.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::13744993287::vessel::d5cca289-fe8c-11ed-889f-43